acilities, and international exposure that will help me develop my technical skills and professional knowledge.\n\nMy parents will financially support my education and living expenses during my studies. I have attached all the necessary documents, including my admission letter, financial statements, academic transcripts, and passport copies.\n\nAfter completing my studies, I intend to return to my home country and apply the knowledge and skills I gained to contribute to the technology sector.\n\nI respectfully request you to consider my application and grant me a student visa. Thank you for your time and consideration.","destinationCountry":"China","intendedEntryDate":"2026-03-12","intendedExitDate":"2026-03-31","status":"granted","currentStage":6,"riskScore":88,"riskLevel":"high","aiAnalysisSummary":"A critical discrepancy exists between the stated destination country (China) and the purpose of visit (Canada), indicating potential fraudulent use of template documentation. The risk is further elevated by a low document verification rate, with only one out of four documents confirmed as authentic.","blockchainHash":"fb9456904898bbdd43d9df79d4c7b2e57f398232a28c480ceb7c7cb660b1c631","blockchainTxId":"0xb37846a476cd148c6850ad9ab44d8bb4","qrCodeData":"{\"visaNumber\":\"VZ20263C262956\",\"hash\":\"fb9456904898bbdd43d9df79d4c7b2e57f398232a28c480ceb7c7cb660b1c631\",\"txId\":\"0xb37846a476cd148c6850ad9ab44d8bb4\",\"blockIndex\":1,\"holder\":\"pasu\",\"visaType\":\"student\",\"expiresAt\":\"2027-03-10\",\"valid\":true}","visaNumber":"VZ20263C262956","grantedAt":"2026-03-10T03:05:58.251Z","expiryDate":"2027-03-10","denialReason":null,"officerNotes":"i think he had valid raeason jhuhuhjiji","renewalReminderSent":false,"createdAt":"2026-03-09T12:42:42.546Z","updatedAt":"2026-03-10T05:09:18.959Z"}]
